data.description: Check out this lovely 3 BR 2 Story home in Rock Island! Walking in, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room with stairs leading upstairs. Off to the side sits the formal dining room which leads into a kitchen with plenty of counter space and cabinetry. There is a door which leads into a small mudroom where you'll get access to the fenced in backyard and attached 1 car garage. Additionally, you'll find a 2nd oversized 2-car garage out back. All 3 bedrooms are located upstairs, each with ample closet space. One of the bedrooms is accessed through another bedroom. Fresh paint through out, you can definitely tell this home has been well-maintained!
